    "However, despite the advantages of simplicity and convenience, there is a significant amount of irrelevant and even harmful information on the Internet that can hinder the work of RALM.",
    "If an effective screening mechanism is not implemented, the effectiveness of RALM will be significantly reduced.",
    "Unlike most studies (Yoran et al., 2023) (Nakano et al., 2021) that directly utilise commercial search engine APIs.",
    "Komeili et al. (2021) propose an alternative approach to using multiple commercial search engine APIs.",
    "They suggest using the Bing Search API to generate a list of URLs for each query."
  ],
